    <title>Using the Usage Analytics app</title>
    <section>
        <para>The Usage Analytics app creates statistics reports of data analytics usage within the
            DHIS 2 system.</para>
        <orderedlist>
            <listitem>
                <para>In the <emphasis role="bold">Apps</emphasis> menu, click <emphasis role="bold"
                        >Usage Analytics</emphasis>.</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
                <para>Select a start date.</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
                <para>Select an end date.</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
                <para>Select an interval: day, week month or year.</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
                <para>Select a category.</para>
                <itemizedlist>
                    <listitem>
                        <para><emphasis role="bold">FAVORITE VIEWS</emphasis>: Number of times users
                            have looked at
                            <?oxy_comment_start author="CPersson" timestamp="20160426T165616+0200" comment="Must define in which apps.
a saved favorite (chart, map or pivto table..."?>analysis<?oxy_comment_end?>
                            favorites.</para>
                    </listitem>
                    <listitem>
                        <para><emphasis role="bold">FAVORITES</emphasis>: Number of
                            <?oxy_comment_start author="CPersson" timestamp="20160426T165827+0200" comment="Must define in which

Consider rewording to &quot;... a saved favorite in the xx, yy ... and zz apps."?>analysis<?oxy_comment_end?>
                            favorites users have created during the selected interval.</para>
                    </listitem>
                    <listitem>
                        <para><emphasis role="bold">USERS</emphasis>: Number of users in the system
                            during the selected interval.</para>
                    </listitem>
                </itemizedlist>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
                <para>Click <emphasis role="bold">UPDATE</emphasis>.</para>
            </listitem>
        </orderedlist>
    </section>
